snippet.textDisplay: "reh guzar ek agar miliye na miliye chalo chalo.... aaso na chalkao..... dard chupa muskao" those word hit SO DEEP! in a society that values appearances above all else and where everyone is running blindly in an endless rat race our most basic feelings and emotional needs that make us human in the first place  have become something to be hidden and buried alive with shame. It's so comforting to know that some people are aware of this miserable situation and Amit Travedi has done a phenomenal job in transforming the meanings that take pages to describe to a 5-minutes blissful song that penetrates every defense and reaches deep into our souls. Simply genius.

Brilliant song, and yet so underrated.
